title: Harley Quinn In Birds Of Prey
description:
Every appearance of Harley Quinn in Birds Of Prey


Issue #27 (Officer Down Part 3: Armed And Dangerous):
While her father clings to life, Oracle gathers Batman's allies: Nightwing, Robin, Azrael, and Batgirl. Their mission: capture Catwoman before the police find her. But the search for Catwoman leads them into an unexpected trap.

Issue #105 (Whitewater Part 2: Permafrost):
Trapped in Russia, the Birds face off against the Secret Six - just as one of her team wrests control of the mission from Oracle! Plus, the return of a very cool character to the DCU!

Issue #106 (Whitewater Part 3: Storm Front):
The Secret Six make their move on the Birds as Oracle struggles to regain control of the team she's spent years building.

Issue #107 (Whitewater Part Three: A Heart Encased In Glass):
A final confrontation pits Spy Smasher's Birds of Prey against Catman's Secret Six in Russia for the soul of one of DC's most beloved heroines! Oh, and Oracle hasn't given up on getting her team back either!

Issue #108 (Whitewater Epilogue: Swan Song):
Oracle tracks down Misfit's parents - but only after a knockdown, drag-out fight with Spy Smasher for control of the Birds of Prey!


Plz Seed!!!
